<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>EasyTradeSetup — Nifty & BankNifty Intraday System</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Trade Nifty & BankNifty with a proven 3-indicator system. TradingView Pine Script + Strategy PDF. Instant download." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg:       #0d1117;
      --surface:  #161b22;
      --border:   #30363d;
      --blue:     #58a6ff;
      --green:    #00c853;
      --red:      #f44336;
      --orange:   #ff9800;
      --text:     #e6edf3;
      --muted:    #8b949e;
      --radius:   12px;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    a { color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      position: sticky; top: 0;
      background: rgba(13,17,23,0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      z-index: 100;
    }
    .logo { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue); letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--green);
      color: #000;
      padding: 0.45rem 1.1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(88,166,255,0.12);
      color: var(--blue);
      border: 1px solid rgba(88,166,255,0.3);
      padding: 0.3rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    h1 span { color: var(--green); }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    }
    .hero-cta {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--green);
      color: #000;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      padding: 0.85rem 2.2rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .hero-cta:hover { opacity: 0.88; }
    .trust { margin-top: 1.2rem; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; }

    /* SECTION WRAPPER */
    section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.9rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .section-sub { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }

    /* PAIN */
    .pain-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .pain-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.2rem 1.4rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .pain-card span { color: var(--red); font-weight: 700; margin-right: 0.4rem; }

    /* STRATEGY */
    .indicator-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .ind-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.4rem;
    }
    .ind-card .num { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--blue); line-height: 1; }
    .ind-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; margin: 0.4rem 0 0.3rem; }
    .ind-card p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.88rem; }

    /* INCLUDES */
    .includes-list { list-style: none; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
    .includes-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.7rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 0.97rem;
    }
    .includes-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .includes-list .icon { font-size: 1.2rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
    .includes-list .label { font-weight: 600; }
    .includes-list .desc { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.88rem; }

    /* PRICING */
    .pricing-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .price-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.8rem 1.6rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    .price-card.featured {
      border-color: var(--blue);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--blue);
    }
    .popular-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: -12px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: var(--blue);
      color: #000;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .tier-name { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .price { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 0.4rem 0; }
    .price-features { list-style: none; margin: 1.2rem 0 1.5rem; }
    .price-features li { padding: 0.3rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); }
    .price-features li::before { content: "✓ "; color: var(--green); font-weight: 700; }
    .buy-btn {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--text);
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .price-card.featured .buy-btn {
      background: var(--blue);
      border-color: var(--blue);
      color: #000;
    }
    .buy-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

    /* FAQ */
    .faq-list { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
    .faq-item {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.2rem 0;
    }
    .faq-item h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .faq-item p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.92rem; }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
    footer a { color: var(--muted); }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      nav { padding: 0.8rem 1rem; }
      .hero { padding: 3.5rem 1rem 3rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav>
    <div class="logo">EasyTradeSetup</div>
    <a class="nav-cta" href="#pricing">Get the Pack →</a>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="badge">Nifty & BankNifty · Intraday · TradingView</div>
    <h1>Stop Guessing.<br/><span>Start Trading With a System.</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      The ETS Intraday Momentum Pack gives you a proven 3-step setup for
      Nifty & BankNifty — with a TradingView script that shows you exactly
      when to buy and sell.
    </p>
    <a class="hero-cta" href="#pricing">Get the Pack for ₹999 →</a>
    <p class="trust">Instant digital delivery &nbsp;·&nbsp; No subscription &nbsp;·&nbsp; Yours forever</p>
  </div>

  <!-- PAIN -->
  <section style="background: var(--surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Sound Familiar?</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Every F&O trader has been here.</p>
      <div class="pain-grid">
        <div class="pain-card"><span>✗</span> You watch charts for hours but never know when to enter</div>
        <div class="pain-card"><span>✗</span> You enter too early or too late and get stopped out</div>
        <div class="pain-card"><span>✗</span> You've bought courses that gave theory but no clear rules</div>
        <div class="pain-card"><span>✗</span> You're profitable some weeks, then give it all back</div>
      </div>
      <p style="margin-top:2rem; font-size:1.05rem;">
        You don't need more knowledge. <strong>You need a repeatable system.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STRATEGY -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>The ETS Momentum Setup</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">3 confirmations. One clear signal. Built for intraday F&O traders.</p>
      <div class="indicator-grid">
        <div class="ind-card">
          <div class="num">01</div>
          <h3>EMA 9 / 21 Crossover</h3>
          <p>Identifies the dominant trend direction. Only trade in the direction the market is already moving.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ind-card">
          <div class="num">02</div>
          <h3>Supertrend (10, 3)</h3>
          <p>Times your entry precisely. Flips green for long, red for short. No guesswork on the signal.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ind-card">
          <div class="num">03</div>
          <h3>RSI Filter (14)</h3>
          <p>Keeps you out of weak or exhausted moves. Only enter when momentum is actually building.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INCLUDES -->
  <section style="background: var(--surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Everything You Get</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">One pack. Everything you need to start trading the system today.</p>
      <ul class="includes-list">
        <li>
          <span class="icon">📘</span>
          <div>
            <div class="label">Strategy PDF Guide (18+ pages)</div>
            <div class="desc">Step-by-step rules, real chart examples, risk management framework</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="icon">📊</span>
          <div>
            <div class="label">Ready-to-Use Pine Script (TradingView v5)</div>
            <div class="desc">Copy, paste, and see BUY/SELL signals on your chart the same day</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="icon">✅</span>
          <div>
            <div class="label">Quick-Start Checklist (1 page)</div>
            <div class="desc">Your pre-trade routine in under 60 seconds</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="icon">📋</span>
          <div>
            <div class="label">Installation Guide</div>
            <div class="desc">Works on free TradingView · 15-min charts · Nifty & BankNifty</div>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING -->
  <section id="pricing">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Choose Your Pack</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">One-time payment. Instant delivery. No subscription ever.</p>
      <div class="pricing-grid">

        <div class="price-card">
          <div class="tier-name">Basic</div>
          <div class="price">₹999</div>
          <ul class="price-features">
            <li>1 Strategy (ETS Momentum Setup)</li>
            <li>1 Pine Script (TradingView v5)</li>
            <li>PDF Strategy Guide</li>
            <li>Quick-Start Checklist</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="buy-btn" href="GUMROAD_BASIC_URL" target="_blank">Buy Basic →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="price-card featured">
          <div class="popular-badge">★ Most Popular</div>
          <div class="tier-name">Pro</div>
          <div class="price">₹1,999</div>
          <ul class="price-features">
            <li>2 Strategies</li>
            <li>2 Pine Scripts</li>
            <li>PDF Strategy Guides</li>
            <li>Trade Journal Template</li>
            <li>Risk Calculator (Excel)</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="buy-btn" href="GUMROAD_PRO_URL" target="_blank">Buy Pro →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="price-card">
          <div class="tier-name">Expert</div>
          <div class="price">₹3,999</div>
          <ul class="price-features">
            <li>5 Strategies</li>
            <li>5 Pine Scripts</li>
            <li>Master Strategy Playbook</li>
            <li>30 Live Trade Examples</li>
            <li>Lifetime Updates</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="buy-btn" href="GUMROAD_EXPERT_URL" target="_blank">Buy Expert →</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section style="background: var(--surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Questions? Answered.</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do I need a paid TradingView account?</h3>
          <p>No. The script works on the free TradingView plan.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Will this work on stocks too?</h3>
          <p>It's optimised for Nifty & BankNifty. May work on liquid large-cap stocks, but we recommend index-only for best results.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>I'm a complete beginner. Is this for me?</h3>
          <p>Yes. The PDF guide explains everything from scratch. If you can read a chart, you can use this system.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How do I get the files after buying?</h3>
          <p>Gumroad delivers your download link instantly via email. No waiting.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Is there a refund policy?</h3>
          <p>We don't offer refunds on digital products. Review the strategy description carefully before purchasing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER CTA + FOOTER -->
  <section style="text-align:center;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Trade With a System?</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--muted); margin: 0.8rem 0 2rem;">Stop trading on gut feel. Get a setup that gives you a clear edge, every single day.</p>
      <a class="hero-cta" href="#pricing">See Pricing →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2025 EasyTradeSetup &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="mailto:support@easytradesetup.com">support@easytradesetup.com</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp; easytradesetup.com</p>
    <p style="margin-top:0.5rem; font-size:0.78rem;">Trading involves risk. Past performance is not indicative of future results. This is not SEBI-registered financial advice.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
